Fashion is a big part of showbiz. This has never been clearer than on the Coke Studio stage where music icons deliver their hits while dressed in killer fashion. One of the major highlights of the show is accessories. Michael Kors views accessories as exclamation points of an outfit. These accessories, ranging from simple items such as hats and statement watches to loud bling, definitely had us exclaiming. We learnt that the busier the outfit the more minimal the accessories.